blogs.title: custom hook에 대하여
blogs.body: Custom Hooks are a mechanism to reuse stateful logic (such as setting up a subscription and remembering the current value), but every time you use a custom Hook, all state and effects inside of it are fully isolated.
blogs.author: 김코딩
